  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Nigeria, accessing justice is an expensive endeavor, bail is &apos;free&apos; yet thousands remained locked up for months sometimes years because of lack of access to legal representation.  Building on success our Abuja based ImpactCove, this project will support the setup of a &apos;LawyersHub&apos;in Nigeria; a co-working community of lawyers with litigation support, pro bono clearing, event centre, related services bringing justice closer to low-income Nigerians, small businesses and nonprofits</narrative>
